Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:16.54,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}你所萌生的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:19.52,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}定是正确无误之志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:22.17,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}我们怀着同一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:26.36,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}却以为彼此道路相左
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:29.65,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}让我们高举那被遗忘的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:32.43,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}踏荒野前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:36.81,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}盈盈微笑 滚滚泪珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:42.33,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}皆不可遗留于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:46.96,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}夏影倒映 白帜高扬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:54.43,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}那是你我的无名之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:59.93,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}在遥无尽头的道路彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:03.23,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}那一线光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.09,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}牵动万千心绪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:08.94,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}深信头顶之青空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:14.18,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}启明星高悬东方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:16.70,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}为我们指引前路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:23.69,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}{\fad(0,800)}梦想必亲手实现
